summary: An ordinance relating to the Water Dept.; authorizing a contract with Masao Nakaso for the sale and removal of Alder and certain other timber from city owned land in Townships 22 & 23 North, Range 7 East, W.M., and Townships 21, 22 & 23 North, Range 8 East, W.M., and Township 22 North, Range 9 East, W.M., in the Cedar River Watershed.
